headline: How Investors May Respond To CMS Energy (CMS) Securing New Data Center Deal Ahead of Q3 Results
summary: CMS Energy announced it will release its third-quarter 2025 results and provide a business and financial outlook on October 30, with a webcast and replay available on its website. A recent agreement to deliver energy to a major new data center is projected to meaningfully increase load growth within CMS Energy’s Michigan service territory.
